---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <span class="text-wave-pink font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">My Story</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-wave-blue-dark mt-2">A little bit about me</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

      <!-- Photo placeholder -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Decorative circle background -->
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-full bg-wave-blue-light opacity-60" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <!-- Avatar -->
          <div class="relative w-64 h-64 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-wave-blue to-wave-blue-dark flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl border-4 border-white">
            <span class="text-7xl font-extrabold text-white select-none" aria-label="Chelsea Seymour initials">CS</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 bg-wave-pink text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg">
            Redcliffe, BNE
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-wave-blue-dark mb-4">Athlete first. Coach because I love it.</h3>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-wave-gray leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I'm Chelsea &mdash; an age-group triathlete, swim coach, and someone who genuinely believes
            that big goals are possible even when life is busy. I work full time, I train around
            shift work, and I know firsthand what it takes to balance it all.
          </p>
          <p>
            I've been lucky enough to race on the world stage &mdash; including a podium finish at the
            Ironman World Championships in Kona and an overall age-group win in Malaysia. Those
            experiences taught me so much about what works (and what doesn't) when it comes to
            swim technique and race preparation.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now I get to share what I've learned. I specialise in video-based swim analysis and
            helping athletes build confidence in the water &mdash; whether that's your first pool
            session or your hundredth open water race. I'll always meet you where you are, and I
            promise to keep it real.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tags -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6">
          {[
            'Age-Group World Champs',
            'Ironman Kona Podium',
            'Video Swim Analysis',
            'Open Water Confidence',
            'Redcliffe Local',
          ].map(tag => (
            <span class="bg-wave-blue-light text-wave-blue text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
